comment: LHH shows that Hawes (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and that Daniels (CHA) and Hawes legally contest Vucevic's (ORL) driving layup attempt.

LHH shows that Roberts (CHA) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Oladipo's (ORL) driving layup attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Oladipo.

Payton (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Walker (CHA) in the backcourt. The two players make incidental contact with one another as Walker begins his dribble.

Walker (CHA) cleanly strips the ball from Payton (ORL).
